OL,3,CChannel Islands extend ID card scheme
OL,4,Cfor French day-trippers until 2025
OL,6,FJersey and Guernsey's governments have
OL,7,Fextended a scheme allowing French day
OL,8,Ftrippers to visit the Channel Islands
OL,9,Fusing only their identity cards until
OL,10,FSeptember 2025.
OL,12,FThe scheme was due to end in September
OL,13,F2024 with visitors from France being
OL,14,Fable to use their identity cards as an
OL,15,Falternative to passports to boost the
OL,16,Fislands' tourism and hospitality
OL,17,Fsectors.
