OL,3,CChannel Islands extend ID card scheme
OL,4,Cfor French day-trippers until 2025
OL,6,FIt was introduced in April 2023 as a
OL,7,Fpilot scheme with both Bailiwicks
OL,8,Fseeing an increase in visitor numbers
OL,9,Ffrom France since then.
OL,11,FThis latest decision was made
OL,12,Ffollowing discussions with the UK
OL,13,Fgovernment.
OL,15,FThe UK government, as well as the
OL,16,FStates of Guernsey and States of
OL,17,FJersey, will introduce an Electronic
OL,18,FTravel Authorisation (ETA) programme
OL,19,Fwhich is currently planned for the end
OL,20,Fof 2025.
