OL,3,CChannel Islands extend ID card scheme
OL,4,Cfor French day-trippers until 2025
OL,6,FThe ETA scheme will mean visitors from
OL,7,Foutside the Common Travel Area (CTA) -
OL,8,Fwhich includes the UK, Republic of
OL,9,FIreland, the Isle of Man and the
OL,10,FChannel Islands - who do not have a
OL,11,Fvisa, will need to provide passport
OL,12,Fdetails to visit the Jersey and
OL,13,FGuernsey.
OL,15,FDeputy Mary Le Hegarat, Jersey's
OL,16,FMinister for Justice and Home Affairs,
OL,17,Fsaid: "I'm pleased to be able to
OL,18,Fextend the scheme for another year and
OL,19,Fso benefit the local tourist industry.
