CT,2,C
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1723218257
OL,3,CChannel Islands extend ID card scheme
OL,4,Cfor French day-trippers until 2025
OL,6,F"Whilst the introduction of the ETA
OL,7,Fscheme makes further extension
OL,8,Fpotentially problematic it will
OL,9,Fincrease the security of the CTA and
OL,10,Fconsequently our island's borders."
OL,12,FDeputy Rob Prow, President of the
OL,13,FCommittee for Home Affairs, said:
OL,14,F"This scheme was initially introduced
OL,15,Fjust for the summer of 2023, but the
OL,16,Fbenefits to local businesses in
OL,17,Fallowing French travellers into the
OL,18,FBailiwick for day trips were clear,
OL,19,Fand so we are pleased to have been
OL,20,Fable to continue it since.
