OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1723218257
OL,3,CChannel Islands extend ID card scheme
OL,4,Cfor French day-trippers until 2025
OL,6,F"France is a country where the number
OL,7,Fof people who hold a passport is
OL,8,Frelatively low, and so ensuring they
OL,9,Fcan still travel following the UK's
OL,10,Fwithdrawal from the EU has been
OL,12,Fvery valuable.
OL,14,F"It is unlikely the scheme will
OL,15,Fcontinue when ETAs are introduced,
OL,16,Fhowever that scheme will increase the
OL,17,Fsecurity of the Common Travel Area,
OL,18,Fand therefore the Bailiwick."
